flowchart TB
  subgraph 检测策略
    R[速率限制]
    S[信誉评分]
    A[异常检测]
    M[多账号关联]
  end
  subgraph 处置策略
    DW[降权处理]
    IS[隔离审查]
    BL[黑名单/封禁]
    AU[审计与回溯]
  end
  R --> DW
  S --> DW
  A --> IS
  A --> BL
  M --> BL
  M --> IS
  S --> AU
  A --> AU
  classDef detect fill:#ffd6a5,stroke:#3c3c3c,stroke-width:2;
  classDef act fill:#ddc9ff,stroke:#3c3c3c,stroke-width:2;
  class R,S,A,M detect
  class DW,IS,BL,AU act

